      "citation_id": "[CITATION_7]",
      "span_text": "We recently proposed such a functional gene grouping approach to test for the combined effect of genetic variants in genes with shared cellular function in the synapse using a manually curated database of gene function based on both experimentation and data mining. Using this approach, it was found that one relay element involved in many pathways (G proteins) was associated with cognitive traits, a strong association, which had remained unnoticed by traditional single-marker analysis."
